The '''Nupchu [[Glacier]]''' is located in the eastern [[Himalayas]] in Nepal.<ref>{{Cite web|title = Glaciers of Nepal|url = http://www.thamel.com/htms/glaciers.htm|website = www.thamel.com|accessdate = 2015-12-21}}</ref> It is north of [[Kanchenjunga]].<ref>{{Cite web|title = Kanchanjunga - The World's Third Highest Peak Summit, Kanchanjunga Expedition - Seven Summit Treks|url = http://www.sevensummittreks.com/packages/Kanchenjunga-86.html|website = www.sevensummittreks.com|accessdate = 2015-12-21}}</ref>

